HEADWORD: Unhallow
<hw>Un*hal"low</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>hallow</ets>.]</ety> <def>To profane; to
desecrate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The vanity <qex>unhallows</qex> the virtue.</q>
<rj><qau>L'Estrange.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unhallowed</ent>⟦br⟧
